%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBT29vQ3.jpg&h=0253f315&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BO2dXv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBO2dXv6.jpg&h=1d53a822&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d946220fc25f963904dc55ddd44c9f25f4bf0a4d","tid":2358032,"uid":59175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\">20210101 五月天 ［好好好想見到你］<br />\nMayday Fly to 2021 演唱會歌單<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 一口蘋果<br />\n2. 盛夏光年<br />\n3. 愛情萬歲<br />\n4. 星空<br />\n5.派對動物 、離開地球表面<br />\n6.愛情的模樣<br />\n7.知足<br />\n8.瘋狂世界<br />\n9.香水<br />\n10.擁抱<br />\n11.聽不到<br />\n12.我不願讓你一個人<br />\n13.如果我們不曾相遇<br />\n14.最重要的小事<br />\n15.永遠的永遠<br />\n16.勇敢<br />\n17.出頭天<br />\n18.人生海海<br />\n19.溫柔<br />\n20.孫悟空<br />\n21.OAOA - 現在就是永遠<br />\n22. 突然好想你<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">23.不愛我就拉倒<br />\n24.說好不好 （with 五月天 陳信宏）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n25.因為你所以我<br />\n26.諾亞方舟<br />\n27.倔強<br />\n28.好好<br />\n29.玫瑰少年<br />\n30.轉眼<br />\n31.笑忘歌<br />\n32.傷心的人別聽慢歌<br />\n33.乾杯<br />\n34.軋車<br />\n35.憨人"},{"pid":"6bedc03c47f567eaf19f9659274a23ad3a4732a9","tid":2358032,"uid":59175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T00:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aG2afm6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaG2afm6.jpg&h=dfade429&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HCFrx8M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHCFrx8M.jpg&h=9ce629c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TN4ctG7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTN4ctG7.jpg&h=3832814f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZAStG7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZAStG7.jpg&h=1394a57b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fusxtG8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfusxtG8